00:01:16,490 --> 00:01:19,920
 And that courage will...

4
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:23,230
 get me out of this hell I am in now.

5
00:01:41,450 --> 00:01:44,570

6
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,730
Zombies are a killer content.

